  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutUs
    class for a description about the developers.
    Inbox
    This class conducts the view Inbox activity, which allows users to open his/her inbox and view messages that he/she has sent to other users.
    MyFriends
    This is the class that returns the friends.
    MyKoinbox
    This is the class that returns the matched users based on our algorithm.
    Outbox
    This class conducts the view Outbox activity, which allows users to open his/her outbox and view messages that he/she sent to other users.
